"0002║$ehgcr220_020m1" = "{Italic}Next, an update on the status of the Purge.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Reporter";
"0003║$ehgcr220_030m1" = "{Italic}Just moments ago, the Sanctum announced{Text NewLine}the successful conclusion of the Purge...{Italic}{End}{Escape}Reporter";
"0004║$ehgcr220_040m1" = "{Italic}...along with the safe arrival of the Cocoon migrants{Text NewLine}to their new homes on Pulse.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Reporter";
"0005║$ehgcr220_050sd" = "{Italic}Yes, that is correct.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0006║$ehgcr220_060sd" = "{Italic}There's no denying the enormity of the strain{Text NewLine}the Purge placed on us all.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0007║$ehgcr220_070sd" = "{Italic}But, given the tens of millions of lives at stake,{Text NewLine}there truly was no alternative.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0008║$ehgcr220_080m2" = "{Italic}Primarch Dysley stood by the move,{Text NewLine}stressing the necessity of the relocation.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Reporter";
"0009║$ehgcr220_090m2" = "{Italic}When asked about the possibility of future Purges,{Text NewLine}the Primarch remained noncommittal...{Italic}{End}{Escape}Reporter";
"0010║$ehgcr220_100m2" = "{Italic}...stating only that he'd seek counsel with the fal'Cie{Text NewLine}Eden and weigh all options before making a decision.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Reporter";
"0011║$ehgcr220_110sz" = "Yeah, that's right. If it makes the Sanctum look bad,{Text NewLine}it never even happened.";
"0012║$ehgcr220_120sd" = "{Italic}In all the centuries since the War of Transgression...{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0013║$ehgcr220_130sd" = "{Italic}...Cocoon has been spared Pulse aggression,{Text NewLine}and prospered for it.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0014║$ehgcr220_140sd" = "{Italic}It is essential that we maintain this peace.{Text NewLine}That is the Sanctum's focus.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0015║$ehgcr220_150sd" = "{Italic}We will continue employing every resource available{Text NewLine}to combat these threats to the harmony of our society.{Italic}{End}{Escape}Primarch";
"0016║$ehgcr220_160sz" = "Meaning, we'll be running for the rest of our lives.";
